    <item>
      <title>[신문으로 배우는 실용한자] 눌변(訥辯)</title>
      <link>https://www.chosun.com/national/nie/chinese_character/2026/04/21/P3SFZ5UD7RDQNPGGSF2LJ5MA2Q/</link>
